# 2efb2358bbce4b2ba21219a675a7dcf3
#: ../../source/15-jersey-client-api-to-access-restful-resource.rst:31
msgid ""
"A new ``WebResource`` is created per RESTful resource that is capable of "
"building requests to send to the resource and processing responses returned "
"from the resource. Each ``WebResource`` follows a builder pattern to specify "
"the required MIME type in the response, application/json in this case."
msgstr ""

